data.description: Welcome home to this pristine end unit that has been beautifully maintained by the seller. Centrally located just minutes to interstates 20 and 285. All appliances includes the washer/dryer to remain. Main level has LVP flooring throughout. Kitchen includes stainless-steel appliances and granite countertops. Very Spacious primary bedroom. Alarm system to remain. Very close to downtown Decatur and East Atlanta Village as well as all Atlanta. Has offer including the Aquarium, the Georgina World Congress Center and Mercedes-Benz Stadium.
